  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the curry powder and cayenne pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chicken and cook until it is browned on all sides.",
    "Add the coconut milk and unwaxed lime juice and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Season the curry with salt to taste.",
    "Serve the curry hot over rice or with roti."
